OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fincreasingly patchy rain will move
OL,7,Fsoutheast across Scotland and Northern
OL,8,FIreland overnight, with clearer spells
OL,9,Freaching the northwest. Meanwhile,
OL,10,FEngland and Wales will be dry with
OL,11,Flargely clear skies and a patchy
OL,12,Ffrost. Some fog in the west.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FEngland and Wales will have
OL,15,Fa dry, warm and mostly sunny day.
OL,16,FNorthern Scotland looks bright,
OL,17,Falthough Northern Ireland and the rest
OL,18,Fof Scotland will stay cloudier with
OL,19,Fpatchy drizzle.
